    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait u said wind is \"far superior\" though... isn't that kind of a strong claim? i thought the whole point was looking at the lifecycle, and i've heard people talk about the massive environmental damage from mining all the materials for turbines and the waste from the blades. shouldn't that be weighed more heavily if we're being objective?",
